quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,99,Nguko uko tukubarira inkuru z’ibyabayeho mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi). Kandi mu by’ukuri twaguhaye urwibutso ruduturutseho (Qur’an ntagatifu)
  20,100,"Uzarutera umugongo (ntarwemere ndetse ntanakurikize ibirurimo), mu by’ukuri azikorera umutwaro (w’ibyaha) ku munsi w’imperuka"
  20,101,"Bazabana na wo ubuziraherezo, kandi uzaba ari wo mutwaro mubi kuri bo ku munsi w’imperuka"
  20,102,"Umunsi impanda izavuzwa, tuzakoranya inkozi z’ibibi kuri uwo munsi zisa n’ibara ry’ubururu (kubera ubwoba bukabije)"
  20,103,Bazaba bongorerana hagati yabo bagira bati “Ku isi mwahamaze (iminsi) icumi gusa.”
  20,104,"(Allah azavuga ati) “Tuzi neza ibyo bazavuga, ubwo ubarusha ubwenge muri bo azavuga ati “(Ku isi) mwahamaze igihe kitarenze umunsi umwe.”"
  20,105,Baranakubaza ku byerekeye (iherezo ry’) imisozi (ku munsi w’imperuka). Vuga uti “Nyagasani wanjye azayiritura ihinduke ivumbi ritumuka.”
  20,106,Nuko (isi) ayisige ari ikibaya kiringaniye (kitagira ikimera)
  20,107,Utabonaho ikoni cyangwa ahegutse n’ahacuramye
  20,108,"Kuri uwo munsi (abantu bose) bazakurikira (ijwi ry’) umuhamagazi (uzaba abahamagarira kujya ku gihagararo cy’imperuka) ntawe unyuranyije na we. Ndetse amajwi (yose) azaca bugufi imbere ya (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe, kandi nta yandi majwi uzaba wumva uretse kongorerana"
  20,109,"Kuri uwo munsi nta buvugizi buzagira akamaro usibye gusa uwo (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe azaha uburenganzira (bwo gukora ubuvugizi), kandi akanamwemerera kuvuga"
  20,110,"(Allah) azi ibyababayeho (ku isi) n’ibizababaho (ku munsi w’imperuka), kandi bo ntibashobora kumumenya wese"
  20,111,"Kandi uburanga bwose (ku munsi w’imperuka) buzaba bwaciye bugufi imbere ya (Allah), Uhoraho akanabeshaho ibiriho byose. Kandi inkozi z’ibibi zizaba ziri mu kaga"
  20,112,"N’ukora ibyiza kandi ari umwemera, ntazigera atinya kurenganywa cyangwa kwamburwa (ibyiza yakoze)"
  20,113,"Uko ni ko twahishuye Qur’an mu rurimi rw’Icyarabu, tunayisobanuramo ibibaburira kugira ngo barusheho kugandukira (Allah) cyangwa bibahe kwibuka"